column16: Desmond Jennings grounds into a force out, shortstop Erick Aybar to second baseman Howard Kendrick.   Jose Molina out at 2nd.
Jose Molina walks.   Sean Rodriguez to 3rd.    Ryan Roberts to 2nd.
Ryan Roberts walks.   Sean Rodriguez to 2nd.
Sean Rodriguez singles on a ground ball to center fielder Peter Bourjos, deflected by pitcher Steve Geltz.
Carlos Pena flies out to right fielder Mark Trumbo.
Elliot Johnson out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Peter Bourjos.   Sam Fuld scores.
Sam Fuld triples (1) on a fly ball to center fielder Peter Bourjos.
Desmond Jennings flies out to left fielder Vernon Wells.
Ryan Roberts flies out to center fielder Mike Trout.
